&lt;p&gt;4）. _&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.edx.org/course/picture-dorian-gray-wilde-berkeleyx-book-uc-berkeleyx-colwri3-4x&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;The Picture of Dorian Gray, Oscar Wilde （王尔德《道·格雷的画像》）&lt;/a&gt;_&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;5）. _&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.edx.org/course/dubliners-joyce-berkeleyx-book-club-uc-berkeleyx-colwri3-5x&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Dubliners, James Joyce （乔伊斯《都柏林人》）&lt;/a&gt;_&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;6）. _&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.edx.org/course/dracula-stoker-berkeleyx-book-club-uc-berkeleyx-colwri3-6x&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Dracula, Bram Stoker （斯托克《德库拉》）&lt;/a&gt;_&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;7）. _&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.edx.org/course/jungle-sinclair-berkeleyx-book-club-uc-berkeleyx-colwri3-7x&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;The Jungle, Upton Sinclair （厄普顿·辛克莱《屠场》）&lt;/a&gt;_&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;8）. _&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.edx.org/course/study-scarlet-doyle-berkeleyx-book-club-uc-berkeleyx-colwri3-8x&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;A Study in Scarlet, Arthur Conan Doyle （柯南道尔《福尔摩斯之血字研究》）&lt;/a&gt;_&lt;/p&gt;

