&lt;p&gt;11）. _&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.edx.org/course/room-view-forster-berkeleyx-book-club-uc-berkeleyx-colwri3-11x&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Room with a View, EM Forster （福斯特《看得见风景的房间》）&lt;/a&gt;_&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;12）. _&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.edx.org/course/call-wild-london-berkeleyx-book-club-uc-berkeleyx-colwri3-12x&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Call of the Wild, Jack London （杰克·伦敦《野性的呼唤》）&lt;/a&gt;_&lt;/p&gt;
